(1, 1, 'DEVELOPER', '<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h3>Well structured UI design</h3>\r\n<div class=\"rating\"><img src=\"themes/jms_yanka/assets/img/icon/star-full.png\" /> <img src=\"themes/jms_yanka/assets/img/icon/star-full.png\" /> <img src=\"themes/jms_yanka/assets/img/icon/star-full.png\" /> <img src=\"themes/jms_yanka/assets/img/icon/star-full.png\" /> <img src=\"themes/jms_yanka/assets/img/icon/star-full.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"desc\">I really like it because of the well structured UI design and all necessary feature were available to build a best e-commerce platform to sell goods.</p>'),
